Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:09.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know the worst thing about you being a Princess of Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:11.50,Spike,,0,0,0,,The dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks for taking care of that, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:17.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,After three events in one week I really needed to relax with a good book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's kinda funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:23.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,All these ponies coming to you for advice about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's funny about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:27.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know, 'cause you used to be famous for being such a bad friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:30.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I had good friends in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.48,0:00:34.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Look at the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:38.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Do you see any photos from before we moved to Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:41.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,And look at you now, the Princess of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:45.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:48.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All my old friends, I can't remember any of their names right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But do you really think that they think I'm a bad friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:55.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well… I only meant that you've come so far, you're a great friend now and…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, I feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've gotta make it up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pack a bag, Spike, we're going to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:05.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And make a list of my friends' names.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,Me and my big mouth…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:54.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on Twilight, you're getting worked up about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The only logical place to start is at the beggining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:12.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's exactly how we left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Look! It's Predictions and Prophecies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And it still opened to the Elements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,And here's that present I was gonna give Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,Guess she won't be needing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:31.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey look, the rest of it is still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How could I let this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:43.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia gave you an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nopony could blame for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:49.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But look at the way I left this place, it's a total mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Just how I left my friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:57.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've got to make it up to…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:03.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,Minuette, Twinkleshine, Lemon Hearts, Lyra Heartstrings and Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yeah… Them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:16.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike! Come on! We've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,Have you been awake all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:24.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I did a little research! And I think I know where we can find Minuette.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That is one of my friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's not too late to forget I opened my big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:39.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike, I'm glad you've opened your big mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,These ponies have probably been suffering ever since I've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:46.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wondering, why their supposed friend would treat them so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Minuette?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.67,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.42,Minuette,,0,0,0,,You old so-and-so!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.00,Minuette,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.71,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.82,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Look at these wings, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.66,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Hey, grab a picture of me and Princess, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:06.17,Minuette,,0,0,0,,I tried to tell my coworkers we used to be friends back when,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.85,Minuette,,0,0,0,,but they've never believed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:17.81,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Wait-wait-wait! Really fluff them up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.19,Minuette,,0,0,0,,So what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:27.13,Minuette,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know you're here all the time, but you never come to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.89,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Hey, I just thought of the greatest idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.76,Minuette,,0,0,0,,You wanna go see Lemon Hearts and Twinkleshine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course! My old friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.38,Minuette,,0,0,0,,It'll be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.31,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.76,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can apologize to all three of them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:48.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Let's hope they're not as traumatized as Minuette.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.68,Minuette,,0,0,0,,She did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:03.25,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Twinkleshine litterally spat out her oats when she heard you're the Princess of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.86,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,We saw you at the coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.19,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,That was some shindig!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.38,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,Sure! Oh, we see you all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.29,Minuette,,0,0,0,,You remember our old friend Lyra, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.15,Minuette,,0,0,0,,She lives in Ponyville, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:19.89,Minuette,,0,0,0,,We're always over there visiting her, or she's coming over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:25.93,Minuette,,0,0,0,,We thought about asking you to join us from time to time, but we just sort of figured you moved on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.52,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,So, what brings you by, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.69,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,All those times you've came back to Canterlot, you've never had donuts with us before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I came to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.24,Minuette,,0,0,0,,For what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:49.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Before I left Canterlot I did not really appreciate my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:53.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and that's because I didn't know how important friendship was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I've learned so much since I moved to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I learned what it means to be a good friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:02.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and that I certainly wasn't one to the three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So for all the pain I've caused you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.57,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:18.61,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Sure, it might have stung a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.02,Minuette,,0,0,0,,when you ran off to Ponyville without saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.43,Minuette,,0,0,0,,but it's not like we weren't used to that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.99,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we didn't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.17,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,But it's really good to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:32.89,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,Hey, anypony up for the blast from the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's our old science lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have so many great memories of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:50.49,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Remember when Lemon Hearts got her head stuck in that beaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:04.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But according to this book, you're supposed to add the sodium chlorate first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.57,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I read ahead and to make a proper solvent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.85,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,you need to add the molasses first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:12.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, I read ahead too, Moondancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and I'm sure it said sodium chlorate first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.22,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've got the wrong book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.16,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,That's so hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Whatever happened to Moondancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:28.26,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,Moondancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know, our other friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:35.31,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, Moondancer! I remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:37.15,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:39.70,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I always liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:42.35,Minuette,,0,0,0,,We just sorta lost touch after you've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:45.74,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,I think she went to live out by the stadium, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.47,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.84,Minuette,,0,0,0,,I think this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.93,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Didn't use to look like this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Moondancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.42,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,What do you want? I'm trying to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's us, your old friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.08,Minuette,,0,0,0,,That's old Moondancer all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.21,Minuette,,0,0,0,,She always did like her books.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:36.55,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Hey, kinda like you used to be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Exactly how I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight! We've been watching her for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Library – house, library – house, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:04.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nopony looks at her or says hello or even gives her a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's like she does not even exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Was she always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.99,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Well, she always was a little shy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:13.07,Minuette,,0,0,0,,but for a while there she was really starting to come out of her shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.35,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Remember when she threw that party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:20.49,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, I think you might have been busy that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.41,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,There you are, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:30.08,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,Moondancer is having a little get-together in the west castle courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.05,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,You wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sorry, girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I gotta lot of studying to catch up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:47.58,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Thought she might finally be letting her guard down a little with that party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.13,Minuette,,0,0,0,,We invited her out a few times after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.65,Minuette,,0,0,0,,but she was always too busy studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.33,Minuette,,0,0,0,,So, eventually, we just stopped asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:58.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I had no idea that party was so important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've got to find a way to make it up to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Moondancer, is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Moondancer, can I talk to you for a mi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.59,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A bubble of silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:44.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you in a while and I thought it might be nice to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.49,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,'cause we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was just hoping we could go outside and talk for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I skipped your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.29,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Why won't you leave me alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.93,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.41,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.08,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I don't have parties!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You did once,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:29.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and I was so caught up on my own studying that I didn't take your feelings into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.17,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Look, Twilight Twinkle…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:31.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:32.58,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.88,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I just need to be alone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:38.10,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,so I can study without some crazy pony trying to make friends, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:42.59,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Wait. How did you get into my book like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've been studying a new studying technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can only do it for a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:54.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But you'll be amazed how much you can pick up when you're actually in a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.76,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,That's one of Haycarte's methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know Haycartes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.78,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Of course! He's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:02.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have a copy of his "Treatise on ponies", you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.89,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is where I used to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:13.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You mean, I never had you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.24,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,A first edition of "Principles of magic"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.18,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Hey. Didn't I give this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:24.23,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I did! Look, I even wrote something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:29.22,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,"To my friend Twilight Sparkle. Thanks for introducing me into the classics."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:33.62,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I can see by the fact that left it here that it meant a lot to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:38.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Look, I didn't bring you over here for even more poignant reminders of what a bad friend I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I brought you here to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can come here whenever you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and study to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:45.98,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But first,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you've gotta do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.08,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Have dinner with our old friends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.85,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I can't, I'm reorganising my biology scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:13:00.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've been spending a lot of time with Minuette, Twinkleshine and Lemonhearts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,since I've been back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They really miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.41,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Look, I've already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.25,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,The last thing I need is a bunch of ridiculous friendmaking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.32,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,keeping me from studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Moondancer, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A wise pony once taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,that there's more to life than dusty old books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.28,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I tried friendship, and it's just not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.01,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Now if you'll excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if I taught you Haycartes method?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.98,Minuette,,0,0,0,,So, what are you studying these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.66,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Science, magic, history, economics, pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:37.59,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.51,Minuette,,0,0,0,,You planning on being a professor or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:41.91,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.75,Minuette,,0,0,0,,So you're just… studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.68,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Moondancer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.63,Minuette,,0,0,0,,It's alright, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.23,Minuette,,0,0,0,,We're having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.47,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Right, everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.89,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Spike, tell Moondancer that story about how Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:03.03,Minuette,,0,0,0,,had to read a book about doing a sleepover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.08,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Slumber 101? I've read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:07.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:12.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, did you know Lemonhearts here works at the Canterlot palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.24,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.07,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,I do the big events mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:18.08,LemonHearts,,0,0,0,,State dinners, that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:31.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Moondancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You've gotta give friendship a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:38.06,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I gave friendship a chance a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:41.89,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,it didn't work out then, it isn't gonna work out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No. No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.93,Spike,,0,0,0,,Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I really messed this one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That party was everything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine what it must have felt like when I didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.10,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Hey Moondancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.80,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Look at this spread, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.58,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.71,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:15.92,TwinkleShine,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't miss one of our best friend's parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:17.46,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Is Twilight coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.89,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:29.74,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Hey, we'll still have fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.58,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If there was only a way to undo the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know what I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I know just who can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.90,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Huh. Guess, they must have gone back to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That! Was! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:18.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We gotta go flying more often Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:19.70,Minuette,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.85,Minuette,,0,0,0,,I thought you threw in the old towel and headed home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I did head home, but not to throwing the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I went to get my secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Minuette, meet…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.30,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.12,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hi, Minuette.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:37.42,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you didn't say Minuette would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.64,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure. She was one of Cadance's bridesmaids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We hang on all the time when she's in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.63,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.82,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself the Princess of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.40,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twilight briefed me on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.95,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We'll need fifteen bags of confetti and as many hooves as we can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.88,Minuette,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.58,Minuette,,0,0,0,,We can pass by the donut place on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,And what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.33,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Oh, "A Brief History of a Wagon Harness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.69,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,"The life and times of Morari the Maneless"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.47,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:48.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.47,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.14,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I don't do parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I think it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Back on we were in school together, you invited me to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was so focused on my studies, that I didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:05.81,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It was a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And now that I realise how important friendship is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make up for my mistake with a new party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:18.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A party in honor of my friend Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:22.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Please, you've got to let me make this up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.82,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,And you think this is gonna do it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uhm… Yes?..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:31.02,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,For sure, why wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.64,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,That was only the first time I ever put myself out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:36.47,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,And then you didn't even bother… to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.64,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Then you left town without saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.96,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Even though we were supposed to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.05,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I was humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.11,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I thought like I was unimportant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:48.70,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to let myself be hurt like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:52.26,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Those three finally convinced me that I had value!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:55.40,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,The other ponies might like me and want to be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.58,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,And you! Didn't! Show! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This party can't make up for the way I hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't let my mistake be the reason you can't be friends with anypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:27.07,Minuette,,0,0,0,,We were your friends then and we'd be honored to be your friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:36.99,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.40,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,That's the librarian,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.75,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,the bookseller,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.12,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:44.15,Minuette,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of friends, Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:47.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:51.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I faced magical creatures, the end of Equestria…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But seeing how my actions affected you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:59.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That was one of the worst feelings I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.97,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:08.52,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,I never realized how much I needed to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.40,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Now. Come on, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.10,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Let's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:23.82,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:24.80,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think, it's time for us to go, Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:53.40,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me make some new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.69,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,Even if they are my old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'll come back and visit soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.28,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,That will be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:03.20,Moondancer,,0,0,0,,You still got to teach me that Haycarte technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:05.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Moondancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:07.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,It got kinda banged up, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:11.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,Here's a little something I wanted to give you back at your first party.
